      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DELIBERATION (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 19.43 beating Angry Goliath. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to his name from nine starts. One of the key runners again. SASSY CROSSED (5) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at Richmond over 320m behind Major Soko (19.15) in a Mix 3/4. Was in the money the start prior. Should be thereabouts. BABY BLOSSOM (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (19.18) in a Mix 3/4 at Richmond. Has ability and can measure up. PRINCE SAL (7) must be included in calculations.",
